summary:
Entrepreneurial eCommerce leader with a passion for building high performing teams, delivering exceptional customer value, driving results and challenging the status quo.

Leader who balances customer focus with data driven business execution.  Ability to zoom in and out to drive and impact at strategic and tactical levels.  Deep go-to-market functional expertise across Europe and North America with multi-cultural general management experience in B2B and B2C internet businesses.

Helped multiple eCommerce companies rapidly scale from start-up to hundreds of millions of Euro/$, gaining market leadership positions in core geographies.  Extensive business strategy, strategy execution and team development experience.
